---
---

<section class="hero-section">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="status-badge">
      <span class="status-dot"></span>
      <span class="status-text">Open to Backend Projects & APIs</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      Hi, I'm <span class="text-gradient">Samir Badaila</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">
      Backend-focused developer from <strong>Nepal 🇳🇵</strong>.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-meta-divider"></div>
    <p class="hero-description">
      I build reliable APIs, automation systems, and data-driven backend services with a focus on performance, maintainability, and real-world usage.
    </p>
    <p class="hero-tagline">
      I enjoy backend problem-solving, reverse-engineering web systems, and automating repetitive workflows.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .status-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    background: var(--accent-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-color);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .status-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background-color: var(--accent-color);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-meta-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background-color: var(--card-border);
    margin: 1rem 0;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
